\n<br />\n港鐵人員正在現場處理，呼籲乘客為行程預留充裕的乘車時間。"},{"pid":"a25b17319860e3621da4cc96ad638d430313fbb2","tid":351821,"uid":2196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T11:03:03.000Z","msg":"又中<br />\n好彩最後兩個站"},{"pid":"251c2fa51703744fb9c00d68d7382c735b7d65f9","tid":351821,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T11:03:18.000Z","msg":"觀塘綫額外行車時間<br />\n<br />\n此訊息發放時間 : 2017-08-08 18:58<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n由於油麻地站附近有信號故障，觀塘綫列車駛經油麻地站至旺角站路段時需要慢駛，觀塘綫來往黃埔站及調景嶺站的行車時間預計需要額外5-10分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n觀塘綫服務更改如下<br />\n黃埔站 往返<br />\n調景嶺站<br />\n每4分鐘一班<br />\n<br />\n現時觀塘綫月台上的乘客較多，候車時間亦會較長。<br />\n請為行程預留充裕時間。<br />\n港鐵職員現正進行搶修工作。<br />\n如有不便，敬請見諒。"},{"pid":"631ae93e696cd5bc908e9aa29111fc09cb199884","tid":351821,"uid":38740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T11:03:34.000Z","msg":"價照加　理能得你"},{"pid":"b74a846cc211f7483eba0e94ce9ab1711be21896","tid":351821,"uid":80461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T11:03:53.000Z","msg":"聽日死金鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1333bd9dee187893ada8b0378ee214cad85da05","tid":351821,"uid":11441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T11:04:06.000Z","msg":"屌 等撚咗10幾分鐘<br />\n呃鳩大家5-10分鐘"},{"pid":"eef8b85d199048ac20287019cb486cd24b5cd474","tid":351821,"uid":1358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T11:05:34.000Z","msg":"垃撚圾地鐵 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 3日壞一次"},{"pid":"98d32ba2c518feea0c19db1810bfc74f2c9cabc0","tid":351821,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T11:06:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e72780c8ba83ea65f9195544574585a203bc6bbc","tid":351821,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T11:06:38.000Z","msg":"港鐵油麻地站信號故障　觀塘線列車服務受阻<br />\n08月08日(二) 18:56<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n由於觀塘線油麻地站附近有一個信號故障，整體行車時間較平日多5至10分鐘。港鐵人員正在現場處理，請乘客為行程預留充裕的乘車時間。"},{"pid":"b8bce2cf9f4511f2063ed368cfdc942152556e23","tid":351821,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T11:07:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ca6ba1490d15cddbbbea23fcdd2f51aea8c9369d","tid":351821,"uid":56160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T11:07:08.000Z","msg":"有冇咁撚廢呀"},{"pid":"0d7154b0a2bf023af30841ccefc41f262764b9ab","tid":351821,"uid":111971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T11:07:40.000Z","msg":"已經停係何文田15分鐘"},{"pid":"3a361d158aa28be1d914953f5812cdb28ce24f15","tid":351821,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T11:07:43.000Z","msg":"廢鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1c3657b18ca9e2b28983b75107d879e1e6d1521","tid":351821,"uid":111434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T11:09:41.000Z","msg":"特登搭到調景嶺諗住長坐 點知要落車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eb5031aca6fe81ed6d9cff617f10c0f9fd657de","tid":351821,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T11:09:56.000Z","msg":"【觀塘綫又壞】油麻地站訊號故障 列車服務受阻<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港鐵觀塘綫繼上周六(5日)發生故障10.5小時後，傍晚6時52分港鐵又宣佈，觀塘綫油麻地站附近出現訊號故障，列車行車時間比平日多5至10分鐘。港鐵人員正在現場處理，請乘客為行程預留充裕的乘車時間<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170808/57057143\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170808%2F57057143&d=wAxuK3IIaKUC0PTKA8tUdcPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=4396fde5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170808%2F57057143&h=e708d906\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170808/57057143</a>"},{"pid":"62a3ae7f03e10cbaba85deddf1eaf75b9ea1c944","tid":351821,"uid":12008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T11:11:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>聽日死金鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n港島好少出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n港島都係用大陸車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58ac28312255096300a16f1f5c694b7888b56640","tid":351821,"uid":12008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T11:11:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>聽日死金鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n港島好少出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n港島都唔係用大陸車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"5d4be2d6e5a1984dc087e554e84e82fd13a81622","tid":351821,"uid":29514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T11:13:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>聽日死金鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n港島好少出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n港島都係用大陸車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n遲d全部市區線轉用大陸車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2e1e1357eb8574f59e8701f36de4b17b347a172","tid":351821,"uid":110745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T11:13:49.000Z","msg":"獲獲新鮮"},{"pid":"411f69acfc88b8859750939fc5a1e5d91e736797","tid":351821,"uid":3782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T11:13:58.000Z","msg":"我又中招 屌"},{"pid":"742d49135f7b8d67010d74c731f5a7a17151060f","tid":351821,"uid":32106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T11:14:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/08/191418_27d7c39c1653d8827e69d56a6e7a6c64.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https:/