/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n港島好少出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n港島都係用大陸車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n遲d全部市區線轉用大陸車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n下年到港島線"},{"pid":"5826dda15467907b7244210cadb9a1f44865981f","tid":351821,"uid":53628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T11:23:53.000Z","msg":"屌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n究竟要壞幾多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43a55b91467a166b7f9e0d6d4f72774238dcd8da","tid":351821,"uid":21279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T11:24:11.000Z","msg":"日經"},{"pid":"a7d49be35add11e99947a7a899f63a8dd4a60264","tid":351821,"uid":18725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T11:24:58.000Z","msg":"「又壞車！O晒嘴！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2017/7/1500881820_ma-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2017%2F7%2F1500881820_ma-1280w.jpg&h=ee720d09&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7abe1cf29361b4246014f8472bd2cab050f6c61f","tid":351821,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T11:25:38.000Z","msg":"觀塘綫額外行車時間<br />\n<br />\n此訊息發放時間 : 2017-08-08 19:15<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n由於油麻地站附近有信號故障，觀塘綫列車駛經油麻地站至旺角站路段時需要慢駛，觀塘綫來往黃埔站及調景嶺站的行車時間預計需要額外5-10分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n觀塘綫服務更改如下<br />\n黃埔站 往返<br />\n油麻地站<br />\n每10分鐘一班<br />\n<br />\n油麻地站 往返<br />\n調景嶺站<br />\n每4分鐘一班<br />\n<br />\n現時觀塘綫月台上的乘客較多，候車時間亦會較長。<br />\n請為行程預留充裕時間。<br />\n港鐵職員現正進行搶修工作。<br />\n如有不便，敬請見諒。"},{"pid":"83fd42e6e4895ce6e30b0fba9a6aedf35a549011","tid":351821,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T11:40:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/08/193805_bafdc966bae7452bddaa574850c14313.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F08%2F193805_bafdc966bae7452bddaa574850c14313.jpg&h=a413fda5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bcd12257fa5a30601c24385e4f3770b0fef00f42","tid":351821,"uid":22974,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T11:43:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8185a02345688f76fcf206fb045a4c2ac7efc5ff","tid":351821,"uid":112308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T11:44:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/08/193805_bafdc966bae7452bddaa574850c14313.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F08%2F193805_bafdc966bae7452bddaa574850c14313.jpg&h=a413fda5&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有無人發起星期六日杯葛港鐵行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91cadfe48c67cae4f19cfdd4c1ac74a178860dfd","tid":351821,"uid":1159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T11:45:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/08/193805_bafdc966bae7452bddaa574850c14313.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F08%2F193805_bafdc966bae7452bddaa574850c14313.jpg&h=a413fda5&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n馬時享咁低</blockquote><br />\n佢虛位元首嚟"},{"pid":"a181e05edf73466dc6276474df7a7df6dbdcd54e","tid":351821,"uid":35285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T11:47:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"97e69a458378a67e6f65a47fa3b70fe6679976bb","tid":351821,"uid":20522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T11:47:38.000Z","msg":"點解綠線可以隔日壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6c0cde998ab84983d5f2a6890a05c380f617ab1","tid":351821,"uid":36178,"like":0,"